public static final class DxJoint.Info1 extends Object
info returned by getInfo1 function. the constraint dimension is m ( ≤ 6). i.e. that is the total number of rows in the jacobian. `nub' is the number of unbounded variables (which have lo,hi = -/+ infinity).
